                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day per bead",
                    "effect": "You open your fan and turn a bead of your choice. The fan casts a 3-action *heal* spell with an area of a 30-foot cone instead of a 30-foot emanation; the save DC for an undead creature is 28. This spell gains the air trait. The rank of the spell depends on which bead you're turning: the first two beads cast 4th-rank *heal*, the center two cast 3rd-rank *heal*, and the last two cast 2nd-rank *heal*.",
